            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="courses">
            <h2>Courses</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.udacity.com/course/android-basics-nanodegree-by-google--nd803">Android Basics Nanodegree</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/swift-programming">Swift Programming</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/the-web-developer-bootcamp/">The Web Developer Bootcamp</a></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="books">
            <h2>Books</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Clean-Code-Handbook-Software-Craftsmanship/dp/0132350882">Clean Code: A Handbook of Agile Software Craftsmanship</a></li>
